  "description": "The longest arc in the library: 120 seconds of imperceptible linear ramp from chaos to modest synchrony. Peak at 0.4 \u2014 the field never fully resolves. Like watching a glacier move. For installations, ambient sets, and meditative performance. The drama is geological patience.",
